|7 |            └─SHARED HASH RIGHT OUTER JOIN    |              |
|8 |              ├─EXCHANGE IN DISTR             |              |
|9 |              │ └─EXCHANGE OUT DISTR (BC2HOST)|:EX10000      |
|10|              │   └─PX BLOCK ITERATOR         |              |
|11|              │     └─TABLE FULL SCAN         |test2(index_2)|
|12|              └─PX BLOCK ITERATOR             |              |
|13|                └─TABLE FULL SCAN             |test1(index_1)|
==================================================================
